<FONT SIZE="+1" FACE="Verdana, Arial"><B>Forum Preferences</B></FONT>
<P>
We use cookies to store your preferences.  Sometimes cookies become corrupted or deleted in your browser.  If so, you may want to delete all cookies that have been set by this forum.  This will mean that all previously saved cookie info will be lost, but it will also mean that any possible cookie problem may be fixed.  <A HREF="http://www.drtwister.com/cgi-bin/ubbcgi/ubbmisc.cgi?action=clearcookies">Click here to delete all cookies set by this forum</A>!</font>
